  "text": "Because of the empirical nature of the transfer functions used, atmospheric corrections are not mandatory if it is safe to assume the atmosphere characteristics are constant over the site. Atmospheric correction could be applied [CITATION_1] if aerosol properties are available (such as those collected through AERONET; [CITATION_2] ).",
